{"tid":955370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【衝路障拒捕，有圖】「毒品快車」機場六車串燒 警犬跳橋追司機受傷 司機遺下26歲年輕女乘客","createTime":"2018-12-25T10:52:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T06:40:58.000Z","uid":20419,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"3a8787d27fd1a567060bfe20a0b58f0bbfc30b45","tid":955370,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E8%BB%8A-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%87%80%E5%85%AD%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%B2%E7%87%92-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-232800765.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25AF%2592%25E5%2593%2581%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E9%25A4%2590%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E9%2587%2580%25E5%2585%25AD%25E8%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%25B2%25E7%2587%2592-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2580%2583%25E5%258E%25BB-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-232800765.html&d=9C3NZCD0Ec3bYwCro%2B320wCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=4c80640f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AF%92%E5%93%81%E5%BF%AB%E9%A4%90%E8%BB%8A-%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E9%87%80%E5%85%AD%E8%BB%8A%E4%B8%B2%E7%87%92-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E9%80%83%E5%8E%BB-%E5%A5%B3%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-232800765.html</a></strong><img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/I92Nn_fz5rqynHKPjaEmtg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/hk01_725/48ac28bb306fed1c71d2f4f9f430b056\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FI92Nn_fz5rqynHKPjaEmtg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2g9NjAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fhk01_725%2F48ac28bb306fed1c71d2f4f9f430b056&h=3322f26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【衝路障拒捕】「毒品快餐車」機場六車串燒　勇警跳橋追司機受傷<br />\n「毒品快餐車」逃走釀六車相撞。周二（25日）聖誕節清晨，新界南交通特遣隊在青葵公路往機場方向近長青隧道入口設置路障，作隨機呼氣測試。約4時許，一輛灰色七人車被截停時未有停下，警方立即進行追截，當七人車途至青嶼幹線收費廣場時，一度發生車禍，撞倒兩個雪糕筒，但司機未有停下，繼續往機場方向狂飆。<br />\n<br />\n警追近25公里 毒品快餐車撞的士<br />\n<br />\n七人車一直駛至機場南交匯處，經港珠澳大橋往機場方向時再回頭，雙方追截近25公里至暢航路一號客運大樓對開時，七人車失控狂撼前面一輛的士，的士再被推前撞向一輛白色GOGOVAN，而尾隨七人車的三輛警車同告收掣不及相撞，引發六車「串燒」。<br />\n<br />\n勇警追疑人跳橋 女乘客束手就擒<br />\n<br />\n意外後七人車司機疑見前無去路，立即離開車廂，從客運大樓L8層橋面跳落下逃去無蹤，1名警員尾隨跳下追捕時受傷。警員事後截獲車上一名女乘客，並在車內搜出100克冰毒，涉嫌販賣危險藥物及擅取交通工具被捕。事件中一名警員及的士司機受輕傷送院。警方正追緝涉案的中國籍七人車男司機下落，他年約40至50歲，當時身穿灰色衣服、黑色褲及米色斜孭袋。<br />\n<br />\n點擊瀏覽《香港01》更多內容和圖集"},{"pid":"e35b1a6b42a3f6b261cf657e30032bdf56b356e4","tid":955370,"uid":20419,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T10:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248332/org/0cc0678572138879b3cf86fad57b93dc.jpg/mAigP1C8t4HwAUo9VBN9ds_ScPiPON5-fZpGYX2aRmE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2248332%2Forg%2F0cc0678572138879b3cf86fad57b93dc.jpg%2FmAigP1C8t4HwAUo9VBN9ds_ScPiPON5-fZpGYX2aRmE&h=addb127a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248287/org/beec57567e0d7db961a8387bad0a1c8e.jpg/_LEF3LKDTaQTNu3uCRuJ5PcFrSTg46Y5_KpwFdaqcBU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2248287%2Forg%2Fbeec57567e0d7db961a8387bad0a1c8e.jpg%2F_LEF3LKDTaQTNu3uCRuJ5PcFrSTg46Y5_KpwFdaqcBU&h=94b6b77c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248286/org/f78b504d2f0f5cff4a81f802b5004551.jpg/oaSJYSXdWtuTPBIcIPpRxrpuLm8cMm-Sd-N7jV3je40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2248286%2Forg%2Ff78b504d2f0f5cff4a81f802b5004551.jpg%2FoaSJYSXdWtuTPBIcIPpRxrpuLm8cMm-Sd-N7jV3je40&h=8668b4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2248324/org/0353284e3c9d88af0c29d30e0ff8e885.jpg/3rm7uifQz7otllS1z9qK-4Ysgd3KiuGfUIMW7FCDFuw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.c